  "title": "Utilities Technician (MNC / west) #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Monitor, operate, and maintain utility systems and production equipment such as Boiler steam generation system, Wastewater Treatment Plant (WWTP); Odour Containment System with chemical scrubber; Reverse Osmosis (RO) water system; Chillers etc</li><li>Ensure all utility systems and production equipment start and operate efficiently and reliably.</li><li>Conduct regular maintenance activities such as chemical top-ups for systems like WWTP and chemical scrubber. Removal and proper disposal of waste residues, such as flocculated sludge in WWTP</li><li>Perform Periodic inspection and preventive maintenance of all systems and production equipment</li><li>Perform functional checks and monitor key operating parameters, maintaining accurate records.</li><li>Execute primary maintenance programs and promptly identify early signs of malfunction or wear, reporting issues to superiors.</li><li>Coordinate and liaise with vendors and contractors for maintenance works, spare parts procurement, and chemical supplies.</li><li>Oversee contractor-led instrument calibration programs for utility systems and production equipment.</li><li>Other ad hoc duties assigned</li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>West</li><li>Open to perform 12 hour shift</li><li>Basic up to 4k + shift allowance</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)<br />Company EA Licence number : 99C4599<br />Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
